{"tid":1141560,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[新．櫻花大戰．卍解] 【FAMI通《新．櫻花大戰》開發成員采訪要點】","createTime":"2019-05-06T14:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T15:32:32.000Z","uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc2aa767fba8986183f8c6adcb4431d7f30da2e9","tid":1141560,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:21:40.000Z","msg":"【FAMI通《新．櫻花大戰》開發成員采訪要點】<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFAMI通公布了對《新櫻花大戰》開發成員片野徹、寺田貴治與大坪鉄彌進行了采訪，詢問了與本作有關的內容。以下，要點總結：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n● 正式確定要做這一作之前其實每年都有提出新企劃，比如京都篇和未來篇之類的。不過最終決定做新作的契機是2016年SEGA Fes上獲得玩家投票第一名；<br />\r\n<br />\r\n● 開發組為《新・櫻花大戰》畫了有300多個LOGO；<br />\r\n<br />\r\n● 找久保帶人來畫人設的原因是因為他也是畫「和服+日本刀」題材的，但主角的刀不會變形；<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"color: red;\">● 久保帶人負責的是人設原案，之後做成3D建模時找了負責動畫版「死神」的角色設計的工藤昌史來做了角色視覺設定。所以看著像「死神」不能完全說是久保帶人的鍋&hellip;&hellip;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n● 除了3DCG的過場以外，遊戲裡還有共計40分鐘以上的動畫過場；<br />\r\n<br />\r\n● 為主角配音的阿座上洋平的台詞量是單個女主角的5倍，「帝國華撃団、出撃せよ！」這句台詞都喊了十幾遍。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EZPjOp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EZPjOp.jpg&h=e7e751b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64af4989a77f052d45294bea2a5b79b349e56e93","tid":1141560,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"唉。。。啲人設1代真係無敵<br />\n呢隻都係睇YouTube 好<br />\n<br />\n但睇啲人溝女好怪"},{"pid":"cc744fcbb3ca77f7593d2a324599b1913bc9ba2c","tid":1141560,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64af4989a77f052d45294bea2a5b79b349e56e93","tid":1141560,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"唉。。。啲人設1代真係無敵<br />\n呢隻都係睇YouTube 好<br />\n<br />\n但睇啲人溝女好怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:25:47.000Z","msg":"假如忽然有興趣玩，條女已被YouTube r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06116ff2f4d2177e1c686cdb1708ece2adfce52","tid":1141560,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64af4989a77f052d45294bea2a5b79b349e56e93","tid":1141560,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"唉。。。啲人設1代真係無敵<br />\n呢隻都係睇YouTube 好<br />\n<br />\n但睇啲人溝女好怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"左下果個係AI醬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3HmbBx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3HmbBx.png&h=712e8754&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42a4e375ba9dc1e4e2ba7e981822ec730c4378cc","tid":1141560,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T23:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6720db75598d25cffa0d09019726e8aac481d795","tid":1141560,"uid":25367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T23:20:30.000Z","msg":"見識完依套人設之後，開始覺得其實紐育星組都幾靚"},{"pid":"a784793642b44a6a473fc2140765dca1637b7567","tid":1141560,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:59:59.000Z","msg":"覺得無咩野，人設正正常常<br />\n<br />\n從未玩過櫻花大戰<br />\n但由細聽到大呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ee85e00ffad5da162c7a809def534ebbf4278e","tid":1141560,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6720db75598d25cffa0d09019726e8aac481d795","tid":1141560,"uid":25367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T23:20:30.000Z","msg":"見識完依套人設之後，開始覺得其實紐育星組都幾靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:02:57.000Z","msg":"藤島功力勁太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc653beca9fccf883a86cdc17bffa958e09be33","tid":1141560,"uid":9924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"最鐘意第一代<img src